data.name: SqlUpdateCommand1.CommandText
data.value: UPDATE [Movie] SET [Title] = @Title, [Director] = @Director, [Actor1] = @Actor1, [Actor2] = @Actor2, [Language] = @Language, [Rating] = @Rating, [Genre] = @Genre, [Release_year] = @Release_year, [Poster] = @Poster WHERE (((@IsNull_Title = 1 AND [Title] IS NULL) OR ([Title] = @Original_Title)) AND ((@IsNull_Director = 1 AND [Director] IS NULL) OR ([Director] = @Original_Director)) AND ((@IsNull_Actor1 = 1 AND [Actor1] IS NULL) OR ([Actor1] = @Original_Actor1)) AND ((@IsNull_Actor2 = 1 AND [Actor2] IS NULL) OR ([Actor2] = @Original_Actor2)) AND ((@IsNull_Language = 1 AND [Language] IS NULL) OR ([Language] = @Original_Language)) AND ([Rating] = @Original_Rating) AND ((@IsNull_Genre = 1 AND [Genre] IS NULL) OR ([Genre] = @Original_Genre)) AND ((@IsNull_Release_year = 1 AND [Release_year] IS NULL) OR ([Release_year] = @Original_Release_year)) AND ((@IsNull_Poster = 1 AND [Poster] IS NULL) OR ([Poster] = @Original_Poster)) AND ([Movie_Id] = @Original_Movie_Id)); SELECT Title, Director, Actor1, Actor2, Language, Rating, Genre, Release_year, Poster, Movie_Id FROM Movie WHERE (Movie_Id = @Movie_Id)
